Tab-Based Navigation Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides tab-based navigation system for mobile applications.
Implements tabbed interfaces with multiple view controllers, tab bar customization,
and tab switching animations optimized for mobile tab navigation patterns.

Key Features:
- Tab bar controller management
- Multiple tab view controllers
- Tab selection and switching
- Tab bar customization and styling
- Badge notifications on tabs
- More tab handling for overflow
- Tab reordering and editing
- Custom tab bar items
- Tab state preservation
- Accessibility tab navigation
- Platform-specific tab styles
- Tab bar visibility control

Provides complete tab navigation system for building organized mobile
applications with multiple sections and proper tab management.
:End Note

